trans-unit.target: TEXT_FESNYRAMBASSADOR2014_00144_HORSEMISSIONARY_000_000<tab>In celebration and calculation do we bring a Heavensturn gift, from the Far East to Eorzea. Long may we be of good blood!

TEXT_FESNYRAMBASSADOR2014_00144_HORSEMISSIONARY_000_010<tab>Has <var 08 E905 ((m'lady)) ((m'lord)) /var> perhaps misplaced the gift <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> was given, that which the giver and the gifted alike call the uma kabuto?

TEXT_FESNYRAMBASSADOR2014_00144_HORSEMISSIONARY_000_011<tab>You are a <var 08 E905 ((woman)) ((man)) /var> fearless and clueless to lose an item of such import! I shall give you another, but misplace it not again.
